text: Daughters of Eve may refer to: * Daughters of Eve, a UK-based non profit organisation that works to protect girls and young women who are at risk from female genital mutilation * Daughters of Eve (band), an American all-female garage rock band * Daughters of Eve (novel), a 1979 novel by Lois Duncan ==See also== * Daughter of Eve, an album from Swedish pop and country singer Jill Johnson
title: Daughters of Eve (disambiguation)
